i[Traditional TLD list](https://github.com/rfc1036/whois/blob/next/tld_serv_list),		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i[New gTLD list](https://github.com/rfc1036/whois/blob/next/new_gtlds_list)		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
